                            <comment id="13705620" author="romain.manni-bucau" created="Thu, 11 Jul 2013 10:00:18 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;A patch handling it with the following strategy:&lt;br/&gt;
1) if the persistence.xml exists -&amp;gt; nothing&lt;br/&gt;
2) else try in TCCL, if found -&amp;gt; use it&lt;br/&gt;
3) else try in compiler artifacts&lt;br/&gt;
3) else try in runtime artifacts&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When found the persistence.xml is copied in target/openjpa-work  to ensure it is a File.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13705650" author="struberg" created="Thu, 11 Jul 2013 11:09:14 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;sounds great, will look at the patch in the afternoon and apply it if it works.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13705772" author="romain.manni-bucau" created="Thu, 11 Jul 2013 13:59:13 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;just saw the workDir field i added uses @parameter expression=&quot;$&lt;/p&gt;
